# Hand Gesture Detection — Custom YOLOv8 Object Detection System

**AI Summer Fellowship 2026 — Computer Vision Engineering Track, Week 2**

A custom-trained YOLOv8 object detection system that recognizes 5 hand gestures in real time via webcam. This repository covers the full pipeline: dataset collection, annotation, training, evaluation, experimentation, and a deployed detection application.

