## Assignment 5 — Detection Application

**Stack:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript (frontend) + Python, Flask, Ultralytics YOLO (backend)

**Implemented features:**

| Feature | Status |
|---|---|
| Image Upload + Detection | ✅ |
| Webcam Real-Time Detection | ✅ |
| Confidence Threshold Slider | ✅ |
| Detection Statistics (object count, processing time, confidence scores) | ✅ |
| Video Upload Detection | 🟡 In progress |
| Export Annotated Results | 🟡 In progress |

**Bonus features implemented:**
- Detection Log (live scrolling list of recent detections)
- Dashboard-style stats panel (objects detected, FPS, average confidence)
- Dark Theme (custom black/grey professional UI with amber accent)
- Temporal smoothing to reduce false-positive flicker on live video

See `/app` for the full application code and setup instructions.

