## Installation & Usage

### 1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone <your-repo-url>
cd <repo-name>
```

### 2. Set up the detection application
```bash
cd app
pip3 install -r requirements.txt
```

Ensure `best.pt` (trained model weights) is present in the `app/` folder.

### 3. Run the backend
```bash
python3 app.py
```

### 4. Open the frontend
Open `app/index.html` in your browser, click **Start Camera**, and grant camera permission.

